name.ja: サイバース・ディセーブルム

text.en:
1 Cyberse Ritual, Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, or Link Monster + 1 Cyberse monster
During your Main Phase: You can Special Summon 1 Cyberse monster from your hand, then you can make this card's Level become that monster's. When your opponent activates a Spell/Trap Card or effect while you control a Link-4 or higher Cyberse monster (Quick Effect): You can banish this card from your field or GY; negate the activation. You can only use each effect of "Cyberse Disabwurm" once per turn.

materials: 1 Cyberse-Type Ritual, Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, or Link Monster + 1 Cyberse-Type monster
